", "bbox": [1105.2, 1221.4, 1141.7, 1244.5]}, {"text": "Other personal premiums grew in 2013, although at a slower pace than in 2012. Premium trends for this line of", "bbox": [104.2, 1294.2, 1127.8, 1317.4]}, {"text": "business have generally tracked with the growth in our personal auto and homeowner lines before the effects of", "bbox": [104.2, 1319.2, 1136.8, 1342.4]}, {"text": "reinsurance. Most of our other personal coverages are endorsed to homeowner or auto policies. In addition to", "bbox": [104.2, 1344.2, 1118.5, 1367.4]}, {"text": "umbrella liability coverage, our other personal lines policies provide property-oriented coverages such as dwelling", "bbox": [104.2, 1369.2, 1153.2, 1392.4]}, {"text": "fire and inland marine.", "bbox": [104.2, 1394.2, 310.3, 1417.4]}, {"text": "Loss and loss expense ratios in 2013 continued at a profitable level, in part due to lower catastrophe losses and", "bbox": [104.2, 1444.2, 1138.3, 1467.4]}, {"text": "noncatastrophe weather. Reserve development on prior accident years provided less benefit in 2013 than in 2012,", "bbox": [104.2, 1469.2, 1160.3, 1492.4]}, {"text": "although development can fluctuate significantly for this business line because personal umbrella liability coverage", "bbox": [104.2, 1494.2, 1162.5, 1517.4]}, {"text": "is a major component of other personal losses.", "bbox": [104.2, 1519.2, 536.1, 1542.4]}]}